What can you do to support someone who has experienced an anti-LGBTIQ hate crime? 
 
Keep your 👁#EyesOpen to spot any signs of violence and encourage them to reach out to a support centre. 

Find a list of support organisations in the EU here: https://victims-rights.campaign.europa.eu/en/organisations

Online shopping can get tricky. But your #ConsumerRights protect you from surprise costs and unfair practices by manufacturers.

Our infographic provides you with key insights into your rights as consumers.
